-code/">earlier this year</a>, by scanning the codes at the door to check in attendees.</p><p>Development on the apps <a title="Event Espresso app development begins" href="http://eventespresso.com/2011/02/iphone-android-onsite-check-in-app-development/">began</a> a couple of months ago. The completed apps should be showing up in their respective app stores in the next couple of weeks. What do you think of the screenshots? And how many WordPress plugins would you like to see mobile apps developed for?</p><p><a href="http://wpcandy.com/previewed/the-upcoming-event-espresso-iphone-and-android-apps/attachment/img_0115" title="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 01"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://wpcandy.com/files/2011/04/IMG_0115-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 01" title="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 01" /></a><br /> <a href="http://wpcandy.com/previewed/the-upcoming-event-espresso-iphone-and-android-apps/attachment/img_0116" title="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 02"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://wpcandy.com/files/2011/04/IMG_0116-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 02" title="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 02" /></a><br /> <a href="http://wpcandy.com/previewed/the-upcoming-event-espresso-iphone-and-android-apps/attachment/img_0117" title="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 03"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://wpcandy.com/files/2011/04/IMG_0117-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 03" title="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 03" /></a><br /> <a href="http://wpcandy.com/previewed/the-upcoming-event-espresso-iphone-and-android-apps/attachment/img_0120" title="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 04"><img width="150" height="150" src="http://wpcandy.com/files/2011/04/IMG_0120-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Event Espresso mobile app screenshot 04" title="E