 the very best coaches and facilities for our athletes because we want them to be coached at par with able-bodies sportspersons," he said. Fintan is the physiotherapist of the Irish Paralympics team. In this case, I think they\'re lucky to be lead by the blind.', 'Finding my blind faith', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '7-revision-12', '', '', '2010-10-23 05:51:39', '2010-10-23 05:51:39', '', 7, 'http://web3.cmmt.ubc.ca/dev/uncategorized/7-revision-12/', 0, 'revision', '', 0); 
